    {
      "sort": 300000,
      "name": "Bloodlust",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "iHjm9GxHYgA4lg9s",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>When a skumdog or creep gains the Bloodlust condition they have zero regard for their own life and the lives of their companions. Everyone is a target and they will fight to the death. While having the Bloodlust condition, the skumdog will never retreat combat and will kill or be killed. This effect lasts 1D6-Brains mod or until he sheds 10HP worth of blood.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1,
        "l18XFo7VCP3jkSA6": 3
      },
