    {
      "sort": 400000,
      "name": "Cursed!",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "yp7GDlpDVO91cOCt",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>The Cursed! condition is found mainly on weapons, armor, and items. When something has the Cursed! condition the last creature who picks it up AND uses it or equips it, or tries to determine what it does cannot drop it. Some cursed things fuse with the body and the user is physically unable to drop it, while others deceive the mind of the user in thinking they cannot drop it. If a creature is cured the cursed item they are holding dissolves into black sand.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
