    {
      "sort": 500000,
      "name": "Dazed",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "7rsMS8SopLGXIITx",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A dazed skumdog rolls a [[/save resolve]] during the next Check Conditions Phase. <span class=\"s1\">If successful, they are no </span>longer dazed and they take their turn as normal.<span class=\"s2\"> If failed they </span>spend the turn seeing stars. This effect only lasts the one turn unless otherwise stated.</p>"
      },
