    {
      "sort": 700000,
      "name": "Drunk",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "tqf12qu9KwS1NONv",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Drinking the fermented blood of a mummy or reveling in the latest victory comes with a price. Intoxication hinders the ability to dodge attacks or land attacks. While drunk skumdogz suffer a -2 penalty to all Prowess checks, Agility saving throws, and attack rolls. In addition skumdogz gain a <span class=\"s1\">+1 bonus to Attitude, a 20% </span>chance to gain the following: +4 bonus to Burliness and immunity to Fear and Madness.</p>"
      },
