    {
      "sort": 650000,
      "name": "Madness",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "MP8G8pm2rVgrwPf3",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Many things can cause Madness. It can incur in many ways, from the gaze of an otherworldly being or the foul breath of a long-forgotten Lich king or even attempting to read a cursed scroll. It is the breaking of a man’s mind. Throughout their adventuring career a skumdog will gain Madness points. If a skumdog reaches a total of 10 Madness points they become insane and must retire from adventuring.</p>"
      },
