    {
      "sort": 900000,
      "name": "Paranoia",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "RL4T0Eth5NKK05eJ",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A skumdog who suffers from paranoia auto-fails any reaction rolls they make to aid another ally, and they cannot help another ally in any capacity. If a skumdog incurs 2 Paranoia condition points they can no longer trust anyone and must retire from adventuring. (NOTE: Paranoia condition points are permanent, but a skumdog can be “cured”)</p>"
      },
