    {
      "sort": 1000000,
      "name": "Petrified",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "wk79mILlDzXEqAEr",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A skumdog is turned to stone. They cannot move or do any sort of action, ever. This can only be cured by a Remove Curse prayer, Wish spell, or drinking a cold refreshing can of Glug-Chug Brand Energy Drink (O.G. Recipe).</p>"
      },
