    {
      "sort": 1100000,
      "name": "Prone",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "Ub7F3RDnX9gdMr8O",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A skumdog falls and can’t get up. The condition Prone differs from the missile attack prone in that it is not intentional. As a penalty, they must use an action to get back up. (Sometimes vs an [[/save agility]]) In addition, the prone skumdog gets a -4 penalty to their AC. This differs from the missile attack prone as that does not cost an action to get back up.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
