    {
      "sort": 1200000,
      "name": "Sugar Rush",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "h0qGxbscphm6gfV8",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>While on a sugar rush the skumdog gains an additional +5ft to movement speed and an additional +1 to attack and a +1 to AC. These bonuses last for one turn. Then comes the CRASH. The turn after a SUGAR RUSH the skumdog suffers a -5ft to movement speed a -1 to attack and a -1 to their AC. They may offset the CRASH by taking more items granting the SUGAR RUSH condition. However, the CRASH will catch up and the skumdog suffers turns of CRASH equal to the amount of turns they had with the SUGAR RUSH.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
