    {
      "sort": 1300000,
      "name": "Unconscious",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "6sDpAU4V5ND4DCaf",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Whether it be from a spell or 0 hit points, an unconscious skumdog falls prone. Since they are lifeless on the ground and can do nothing to defend themselves, any creature can approach them and make a Coup de Grace Attack. An ally can heal them using spells, potions, vitality sticks, etc to bring them to 1HP. If they do, then the skumdog is no longer unconscious and may perform actions and move on their next turn. (NOTE: At the beginning of the next turn, they are @UUID[.Ub7F3RDnX9gdMr8O]{Prone} according to the description above.)</p><p></p>"
      },
